                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " NEUTRON FLUX DETERMINED USING",
                " A NE102 PLASTIC SCINTILLATOR TO MEASURE THE ALPHAS",
                " IN THE NEUTRON PRODUCING REACTION. NO VALUE GIVEN."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".THE WHOLE ANGULAR DISTRIBUTION FOR THE ELASTIC",
                " SCATTERING WAS ANALYSED WITH A SPHERICAL OPTICAL",
                " POTENTIAL, AND THE CARBON AND SULFUR ANGULAR DISTRI-",
                " BUTION, BOTH FOR THE ELASTIC AND INELASTIC SCATTERING",
                " TO THE FIRST (2+) EXCITED LEVEL, WERE ANALYSED BY",
                " THE COUPLED-CHANNEL METHOD."
              ]
            }
          ],
